Be6 9. Qd3 b5
{ Immediately asking White what he's going to do with the bishop. } 10. Bb3
Nbd7
{ Since the battle for d5 is still ongoing Black prefers to have a knight on d7 with the idea to use it for extra control from f6  (in case White takes the f6-knight)  or b6. }
11. O-O
