Nc6 { The knight comes out to a natural square and Black will castle next. }
13. O-O-O O-O-O { Defending the bishop. } 14. Bb6 Rd6
{ The rook is well-placed on d6 as it eyes the bishop on b6, introducing various knight jumps to d4 or b4. The endgame is equal. }
